articles.author: Juliette Jeffers
articles.title: Rihanna Is Ready to Confess - Interview
articles.description: Somewhere on the outskirts of Milan, our EIC Mel Ottenberg comes face to face with his former boss. And for the next 90 minutes, she gives him her all.
articles.content:
Rihanna wears Shirt Dior. Hat Sarah Sokol. Bra Savage X Fenty.
Okay, so its the night after the last day of Milan Fashion Week and Im at a giant arena on the outskirts of Milan to interview my forme… [+26651 chars]
